Subject: Netwrix Support for Mac15 - iPhone Mirroring App
Description:
This is regarding the new app in Mac15 - iPhone Mirroring App. We have observed a logging gap for file transfer using iPhone mirroring application which is included with macOS Sequoia 15 or later.

Is this supported b y current version of Netwrix? If not when is the expected fix for this?
Solution_Comment__c: The feature that the customer requested is available in 5941. They will consider upgrading to be able to use it.
